## üîÑ Synchronisation prod ‚Üí preprod

### Contexte

- **prod** : WordPress production sur VPS
- **preprod** : WordPress pr√©-production sur m√™me VPS
- **Objectif** : Copier donn√©es prod ‚Üí preprod pour tests

### Architecture Multi-Environnements

```
VPS Serveur
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ /path/to/kpi_prod/
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ docker/wordpress/         # Fichiers prod
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ docker/db/mysqlwp/        # BDD prod
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ docker/.env               # APPLICATION_NAME=kpi
‚îÇ
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ /path/to/kpi_preprod/
    ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ docker/wordpress/         # Fichiers preprod
    ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ docker/db/mysqlwp/        # BDD preprod
    ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ docker/.env               # APPLICATION_NAME=kpi_preprod
```

### Synchronisation Manuelle

#### Script sync_prod_to_preprod.sh

```bash
#!/bin/bash
# sync_prod_to_preprod.sh
# Synchronisation WordPress prod ‚Üí preprod

set -e  # Arr√™t sur erreur

# Configuration
PROD_PATH="/path/to/kpi"
PREPROD_PATH="/path/to/kpi_preprod"
DATE=$(date +%Y%m%d_%H%M%S)

echo "=== Synchronisation WordPress prod ‚Üí preprod ==="
echo "Date: $(date)"

# 1. Backup preprod avant √©crasement
echo "[1/6] Backup preprod actuel..."
cd $PREPROD_PATH
tar -czf docker/wordpress_preprod_backup_${DATE}.tar.gz docker/wordpress/
docker exec kpi_preprod_dbwp mysqldump -u root -p${DBWP_ROOT_PASSWORD} ${DBWP_NAME} > docker/wordpress_preprod_db_backup_${DATE}.sql
echo "‚úì Backup preprod sauvegard√©"

# 2. Arr√™ter conteneurs preprod
echo "[2/6] Arr√™t conteneurs preprod..."
cd $PREPROD_PATH
make preprod_down
echo "‚úì Conteneurs preprod arr√™t√©s"

# 3. Copier fichiers WordPress prod ‚Üí preprod
echo "[3/6] Copie fichiers WordPress..."
rsync -av --delete $PROD_PATH/docker/wordpress/ $PREPROD_PATH/docker/wordpress/
echo "‚úì Fichiers copi√©s"

# 4. Exporter BDD prod
echo "[4/6] Export base de donn√©es prod..."
cd $PROD_PATH
docker exec kpi_dbwp mysqldump -u root -p${DBWP_ROOT_PASSWORD} ${DBWP_NAME} > /tmp/wordpress_prod_export_${DATE}.sql
echo "‚úì BDD prod export√©e"

# 5. Importer BDD dans preprod
echo "[5/6] Import base de donn√©es preprod..."
cd $PREPROD_PATH
# D√©marrer uniquement dbwp
docker-compose -f docker/compose.preprod.yaml up -d dbwp_preprod
sleep 10  # Attendre MySQL

# Drop et recr√©er la base
docker exec kpi_preprod_dbwp mysql -u root -p${DBWP_ROOT_PASSWORD} -e "DROP DATABASE IF EXISTS ${DBWP_NAME}; CREATE DATABASE ${DBWP_NAME};"

# Importer dump prod
docker exec -i kpi_preprod_dbwp mysql -u root -p${DBWP_ROOT_PASSWORD} ${DBWP_NAME} < /tmp/wordpress_prod_export_${DATE}.sql
echo "‚úì BDD import√©e"

# 6. Ajuster URLs preprod
echo "[6/6] Ajustement URLs preprod..."
docker exec kpi_preprod_dbwp mysql -u root -p${DBWP_ROOT_PASSWORD} ${DBWP_NAME} -e "
UPDATE wp_options SET option_value = 'https://preprod-domain.com' WHERE option_name = 'home';
UPDATE wp_options SET option_value = 'https://preprod-domain.com/wordpress' WHERE option_name = 'siteurl';
UPDATE wp_posts SET post_content = REPLACE(post_content, 'https://prod-domain.com', 'https://preprod-domain.com');
UPDATE wp_posts SET guid = REPLACE(guid, 'https://prod-domain.com', 'https://preprod-domain.com');
"
echo "‚úì URLs ajust√©es"

# 7. Red√©marrer preprod
echo "Red√©marrage preprod..."
make preprod_up

echo ""
echo "=== Synchronisation termin√©e avec succ√®s ! ==="
echo "Backup preprod: docker/wordpress_preprod_backup_${DATE}.tar.gz"
echo "Test preprod: https://preprod-domain.com/wordpress"
```

#### Utilisation

```bash
# Rendre ex√©cutable
chmod +x sync_prod_to_preprod.sh

# Ex√©cuter
./sync_prod_to_preprod.sh
```

### Synchronisation Automatique (CRON)

#### Configuration CRON Hebdomadaire

```bash
# √âditer crontab
crontab -e

# Ajouter synchronisation tous les dimanches √† 2h du matin
0 2 * * 0 /path/to/kpi/sync_prod_to_preprod.sh >> /var/log/wordpress_sync.log 2>&1
```

#### Script Am√©lior√© avec Notifications

```bash
#!/bin/bash
# sync_prod_to_preprod_auto.sh
# Version automatis√©e avec notifications

# Email de notification
ADMIN_EMAIL="admin@domain.com"

# Fonction notification
notify() {
    echo "$1" | mail -s "WordPress Sync prod‚Üípreprod" $ADMIN_EMAIL
}

# Ex√©cution avec gestion erreurs
if ./sync_prod_to_preprod.sh; then
    notify "‚úì Synchronisation WordPress r√©ussie - $(date)"
else
    notify "‚úó ERREUR Synchronisation WordPress - $(date)"
    exit 1
fi
```

### Synchronisation S√©lective

#### Fichiers Seulement

```bash
#!/bin/bash
# sync_files_only.sh
rsync -av --delete \
    --exclude 'wp-config.php' \
    --exclude 'wp-content/cache/' \
    --exclude 'wp-content/backup/' \
    $PROD_PATH/docker/wordpress/ \
    $PREPROD_PATH/docker/wordpress/
```

#### Base de Donn√©es Seulement

```bash
#!/bin/bash
# sync_db_only.sh
docker exec kpi_dbwp mysqldump -u root -p${DBWP_ROOT_PASSWORD} ${DBWP_NAME} | \
docker exec -i kpi_preprod_dbwp mysql -u root -p${DBWP_ROOT_PASSWORD} ${DBWP_NAME}
```

