## üìö Scripts d'Automatisation

### Script Makefile (Ajouts)

Ajouter dans **`Makefile`** :

```makefile
# WordPress - Backup
.PHONY: wordpress_backup
wordpress_backup:
	@echo "Creating WordPress backup..."
	@tar -czf docker/wordpress_backup_$(shell date +%Y%m%d_%H%M%S).tar.gz docker/wordpress/
	@docker exec $(DBWP_CONTAINER_NAME) mysqldump -u root -p$(DBWP_ROOT_PASSWORD) $(DBWP_NAME) > docker/wordpress_db_backup_$(shell date +%Y%m%d_%H%M%S).sql
	@echo "‚úì Backup created in docker/"

# WordPress - Sync prod ‚Üí preprod
.PHONY: wordpress_sync_preprod
wordpress_sync_preprod:
	@echo "Synchronizing WordPress prod ‚Üí preprod..."
	@./scripts/sync_prod_to_preprod.sh

# WordPress - Restore from backup
.PHONY: wordpress_restore
wordpress_restore:
	@echo "Listing available backups:"
	@ls -lh docker/wordpress_backup_*.tar.gz docker/wordpress_db_backup_*.sql 2>/dev/null || echo "No backups found"
```

### Scripts Complets

Cr√©er r√©pertoire **`scripts/`** :

```bash
mkdir -p scripts
chmod +x scripts/*.sh
```

