## üÜò Troubleshooting

### Erreur "Error establishing database connection"

```bash
# V√©rifier conteneur dbwp
docker ps | grep dbwp

# V√©rifier connexion
docker exec -it kpi_wordpress mysql -h dbwp -u ${DBWP_USER} -p
```

### M√©dias non affich√©s

```bash
# V√©rifier permissions
docker exec -it kpi_wordpress ls -la /var/www/html/wp-content/uploads

# Corriger permissions
docker exec -it kpi_wordpress chown -R www-data:www-data /var/www/html/wp-content
```

### URLs incorrectes apr√®s migration

```sql
-- Se connecter √† MySQL
docker exec -it kpi_dbwp mysql -u root -p${DBWP_ROOT_PASSWORD} ${DBWP_NAME}

-- V√©rifier URLs actuelles
SELECT * FROM wp_options WHERE option_name IN ('home', 'siteurl');

-- Corriger si n√©cessaire
UPDATE wp_options SET option_value = 'https://correct-domain.com' WHERE option_name = 'home';
```

